text: Þis is þæ land boc æt yting stoce þe Eadgar cing gebocode into ealde mynstre.
Ðis sint þara X hida landgemære to Ytingstoce.
Ærest of breting mæde norðeweardre ut on icenan.
Fram brentinge to þære gearn windan fet.
Of ðære gearn windan fæt to stybban snade ðer þær ða twegen wegas tolicgað.
Of þan heale to wifeles stigele.
Of þam burnan to ðam readan fordan.
Of þam forda ut on icena on þet west steð ut andlang þest staðes.
Eft on brenting þær we ær on fengon.
